t dominates the luminosity\noutput. We propose that the available gas reservoir and the individual\nstructure of the interacting galaxies plays a major role in the evolution of\nthe system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Aug 1999 09:19:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-31"}
