s. The symmetry requirement plays a central\nr\\^{o}le in the point-splitting renormalization procedure of the one-loop\nstress-energy tensor in curved spacetimes for Hadamard quantum states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Aug 1999 17:25:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Jan 2000 13:20:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-31"}
